hey guys!

   New LJ...im gonna delete this one soon...or just not use it as much, im not that sure but my new username is:

I was just watching The Little Mermaid....and i got to the part where she turns back into a mermaid...and i just couldnt watch anymore, becuz it made me so sad :-( And they were sooo close to kissing!!! BLAH...I wish i was a princess, because then i would be guaranteed a prince :)

-Jami

Today was F-A-N-T-A-S-T-I-C!!

 Went to the beach w/ Jenn, Sarah & Joe. Like i woke up and they called and then came over...it was weird, cuz i was gonna go with Brittany and meet them up there, but i just went with them anyways. So we got there at like 12. Frolciked in the water, than ate. Then Izzo and Ant came! wow.....Anthony is soooo cute! lol. Then we hung out with them, and I attempted to go skim boarding, bwahaha! I feel twice, and hurt myself, and now my knee and ankle hurt, and my knee is cut. But it was cool. Then we met some more guys. One of which worked at Albertsons...he was super cool! Even tho he kept throwing seaweed at me and they all were like trying to throw fish at me...what is that? Oh well...then Bree, Mike and Ant jumped off the pier...i didnt want anthony to go cuz he might have broken his pretty face,lmao! We went to Bree's hotel room, i washed my hair, and we left. It was such fun. But im EXTREMLY burt, it hurts sooo bad, but w/e, ill get over it! I also dyed my hair...its cute!! Not blonde anymore and im glad :) lol, i still havent seen it all nice and done yet...ill post a pic when i take one :)

-Jami

Tonight.. Jenn is spendin the night, then we r going to see Shrek 2! Mike is gonna go as well :-D such fun we will have!

Well...

 I think i may have somewhat of an idea of whats wrong in life lately... Im stressing over everything...friends, school, life, guard...just EVERYTHING, and its screwing my body up tremendously. This stress is just contributing to everything else. I feel like things r closing in on me, im so paranoid all the time..and i just cant be happy... I know sumthing else is bothering me ALOT...im not sure what it is...Maybe, everyone is making new great friends...and making new cliques, and im just not, and i feel left out? Im not sure... I feel so stupid saying this to my LJ...but i lost my diary,lol. Maybe tonight...i should just sit down and try to think and work things out... Maybe i should start off by apologizing to people? I dunno that i did anything wrong, but maybe i will realize some things when i think tongight. :::sigh::: Finals next week (Gag me) Then colorgaurd all summer, which will be great.. i realized that it makes me very happy... But Alysa told me that ive been giving people attitude...but i TOTALLY did not intend or mean it! Im really sorry to whoever i was doing it to...i really didnt mean it at all... Ugh...i feel horrible about it! Ok well im out...i needa find my retained and put the beast in

Im done...just freaking done!

   I cannot stand anything anymore...i feel so outraged at EVERYTHING... I dont even know how to explain myself at all...im just sick of EVERYTHING...sick of people hurting my feelings...sick of school, just UGH!! And on top of that...my body is being completley out of wack! Its just ridiculious, i feel like a damn emo kid... but thats what i am...im emotional...VERY. Things just arent funny to me anymore. I dont know whats wrong with me? Whatever... 2day, was alright tho...the play went great, mandi and i had lotz of fun :-) Then went home..Joe got me, it made my day completley...that kid just makes me smile, even when i dont want 2. Then try-outs...they went good...but i dont wanna start on those. Well i Jamie sent me this cute pic!I dont look 2 hott, but Kayla does:)

 

 

-Jami

Wurd!

  This week has gotten ALOT better...things have turned out marvelously! This week has been try-outs...the newcommers r doing sooo good! :-) They deff. bring a smile to my face...group 1 ROCKS!! WHAT WHAT! LOL im truly a loser... i made a nametag with the ugly colors cuz i figured no one would use them,lol. AND our play is today and tomorrow...today went well..Mandi Wray and i...we r whats goin! We matched today as well! HEHE!! Its great! Lets see...AWW Ian just saw that video of that guy getting his head cut off...hes like freaking out! I feel horrible for that poor man and his family...ugh :-( 

Tomorrow is Stevens last day :*( Im really gonna miss that kid...he taught me quite a bit,lol...He gave me the best years of his life!

Robbie came in today :) It totally made my day!! Hes just so...dreamy!! Ok well im out byez :-)

-Jami

My boys... Whoa.. I dont think i have ever told either one of u, how grateful i am of both of u...even tho the first time we met...i was just a stupid canadian, lol. We have grown to love eachother...You 2 have been there for me threw thick and thin...threw whatever i have needed...and im so grateful to have u guys. Ian...u have jjust been phenominal 2 me...i truly love u. Nicholas...ahh so many memories... i love u as well...even tho u dont love me, lolol :-D ahh good times with both of u! Thanx guys...u truly r my life

 

-Jami

I had the most spectacular day with my favorite person ever :)

  VK picked me up around 12:30, and we went to Beed O' Bradys and got some lunch...very adult like,lol. Then it was off to GS.. it was time for Battle of the Bands, woo. It was freakin awesome! We had tons of fun...lotz of people there. Chris's band sooo rocked! Me and the girls were jumpin around and being crazy,lol. It was fun :-D Then Krystal Brandon and I all went to the japaneese food place, but they were closed, so we went to Pulix and bought some Cosmo, wooo! Then we went to McDonalds, lol. Brandons new SUV totally rocks!! Its soo soft, Krystal has a yucky car tho ;-D hehe! Im gonna miss those 2... Krystal has become like a big sister to me, i talk to her about everything in the world! And Brandon... lol, he has just been a great friend! Hes a funny one. 

Well... What Lauren said really pissed me off/ and made me open my eyes...talking shit doesnt get u anywhere, and it certainly doesnt do anything. So Lauren thanx...:-/ Im sorry about everything i have ever done to anyone, I guess u could say i am a fuck-up


-Jami

Well this week started good! Band Banquet...TONS of fun...got a Craigateer shirt :-D Then tuesday was a day...hung with Alysa and Sheila, it was fun! Now today fucking sucked... People r so freaking gay...i CANT stand it! Talking about personal shit to other people...and its none of their damn business.. just go to hell...im so serious. Dont ever talk to me, dont try to talk 2 me, cuz i dont wanna hear it. Im done...I was in freaking tears! It was ridiculious!

Joesph rocks as well...today he just made me feel so much better! He kissed my cheek and my hand... It toally made my day...and i LOVED it! :-)

On a better note.. I got my pics developed today :) AHHH they r so cute!!http://schooliscool.mypicgallery.com/ <---LINK!!

Tomorrow aunt and uncle r commin down..it SOOO rocks!!! I cant wait :-)

I love ya Krystal Belle Hofacker...what would i do without ya :-D

<small>
Well! Today was alright... I was jammin out to Sclub7! LMAO...i found their Cd and decided to pop it in... it was fun! MY mom liked her present :-D We got her this cute gold bracelet...and this cute little book! It was super awesome,lol.

Saturday wasnt such a happy day... Some people were supposed to get together and do some stuff.. Well 2 people didnt show, and left me and brittany to do EVERYTHING...Im so dissapointed.. :::sigh::: But im kinda glad...becuz Brittany and I got to bond...and i feel alot closer to her now as a friend... It was a REALLY fun time all in all. But im still really mad/dissapointed at the others...W/e tho.

Tomorrow is band banquet...im so excited, but im not sure what to wear, lol! Such a girl i am.. :-x lol... 

-Jami

Wow! Such an awesome little week ive been having...things have been looking up for me...i think its becuz ive moved on from alot of things...pushed the bad behind me...and i have the best friends ever to help me! Lol i sound like a queer! Oh well... Tomorrow is the last day for seniors...im REALLY going to miss alot of them...specially VK..whoa im gonna cry :*(  And Steven...oh my.. im gonna cry over him as well. Today was sucha fun day tho.. us girls did stuff for the guard :-) It SOOO rocks...i got my outfit for band banquet...Sarah paige and i have the same skirt! Its super cute!! :-D We alsto stopped by to see Hofacker. WE went to youthgroup as well...IT WAS SO MUCH FUN!! lol...i never thought i would enjoy it, but wow it was lotz of fun!! HEHE...i met new people!!! It was a hoot! Ian rocks.. he made my background picture!!! HEHE!! I love it! Ok well its just been a great weekend :)


-Jami

Why do i feel so useless lately? I feel like im more of a burden 2 people than anything. I need reasons to be happy now... before i was just happy. What happened to me? I wish i knew... This sux bad. Bad ass week...not to hott of an ending to the week either. I wish people would stop talking shit about crap thet dont even know about...its freakin pissin me off! ARGH.

Something is going bad between Frankie and I...whatever we had is no more...i dont know what i did...i wish he would tell me...i lost him i think...it hurts 

On a better note-Saw Footloose..Nick was awesome...i had no idea he could do that :-D It made me smile.. Im very happy for him!

-Jami

This weekend was sooo GREAT

Well... Friday went to the movies with Sarah... I met Sam.. she rocks! We saw 13 going on 30...it made me cry...it was a good movie tho. I met some of their friends, Bree(i already knew) Her b/f, Kaity and her b/f. It was alotta fun.Hit on some 7th graders, lmao!!! Then after that went back to Sarahs house. Coit, Kenny, and Brandon were there, hung out with them for a lil while, then Brit. came over. We jumped on the trampoline...almost broke it,lol. Then Pat came over...hes a nice boy! Then we went to sleep...

Saturday
  Well, we woke up at 8, then went to Drum Corp.Camp...HOLY jesus, it was friggin tiring,lol. I could NEVER do that crap ALL SUMMER...mad props to those who do! WE did some riffle stuff...considering i cant even do a drop spin on riffle, lol i looked queer! but w/e. We left early tho...we didnt feel to well. Then we went to Publix, got some chips, ice cream, and drinks,lol, then went to sarahs and tanned on her trampoline... THEN i went home showered, got ready to go to Ritas!! We went glow bowling :-D Ian, Rita, Megan, Sam, Me,Cameron, Patrick, and Sarah Paige all went...it wuz a freakin hoot!! There were some hotties up there as well!!!  lol. i had sooo much fun!!

Sunday
  Well Rita and I woke up, and we watched Jay and Silent Bob, lmfao, it was funny...I left her house not to l ong ago...cuz im goin on my boat today :-D WEEE Im excited i havent been on that thing in ages... 

-This weekend has rocked! Its been the best weekend ive had in a LONG LONG time, thanx guys :-D


*-Jami

Another day... people r becomming SOO distant lately...it sux really bad. But it happens...right? Hmm...guard seems like more of a hassel than a hobby, when i get in that class i feel so tired and negative, i dunno..i used to LOVE that class...but lately its just not workin out like that. I just feel like being beside myself? Its just a phase tho...Im sure once i get things organized again, i will be in a better frame of mind.threw the hardships in life u find out who u really are...and how much u can handle, and im finding out ALOT...im not as strong as everyone thinks i am...or even i think i am.. some nights i just cry over everything, i feel good after a good cry. It clears my head. You also find friends u never thought u had.. one person i have gotten SOO close to is Ian...i would trust him w/ my life, he is just spectacular... He is truly amazing. He is just so great to talk 2. Im hangin with Rita this weekend!! I havent hung with her in a LONG time...and now it seems like everyone is going to drum corp. camp thingy...i feel bad, cuz i wanted to go in the beginning, but no one else did, so i made plans...and imnotgonna change them, ive been looking forward to this all week :-D Me and RiRi!! AWESOME! And Krysten...wow, she just rocks my socks all over... I love her! Mandi Wray and I wrote love letter 2day...it was so much fun, i like acting EXTREMLEY childish every now and then...lol...ok well ALOT! alrighty well im out :-D

-Jami

Well...today was rockin my sox totally!

   Played B-ball w/ Mary 1st period...we were SOO ballers!! Lol! Then had drama..u know me and Mandi Wray r the center of the play, lmao...j/k! Well.. I proposed to Nicholas today,lol and he accepted :-D! But then the ring got stuck...and we had to lotion it off...we were jackin his finger off,lol. it was humerous!!! BUT he broke my heart in 5, and declined the marriage... i almost cried, but he wanted to go on the honeymoon.HA! what kind of a girl does he think i am? lol. Its more complicated "playin the feild" than i thought.. So many wonderful guys! Went to Casies after school today...it was fun, watched some old videos. Alec wasnt there today tho! Well Ian, is rockin as usual...always makin me feel better. I cant wait till this weekend with Rita...tons of fun :-D MWAHAH!! Ok well im outta here :-D Byez


-Jami

I feel so...shitty. I havent gone threw a state like this in a long time. Moving on has been ALOT harder than what i said...but Ashley's advice has really helped putme in the right frame of mind. He was my 1st love...i guess i dont have room 2talk...i did break up with him...but there were so many reasons behind it tho. People like to jump to conclusions tho! W/e...its my life not theirs. I have come to realize that one of my main priorities is to see other people happy...I mean...i like 2 be happy, but its just not something i really focus on? hmm.. well enuff of this sadness...Nick came back :-D I was so happy seeing him today! Him and Ian...they r my best guy friends...they keep me leverl headed! 


-Jami

Well...After EVERYTHING...i FINALLY made it 2 prom,lol...so many odds against me!

Dinner...
Got there and waited for 20min. till tammi got there, at first they didnt have us down damnit! So i put our name on the list, Alysa and Alex showed up and we waited for about 45-50 min. And got our table! I was sooo jumpy,lol. Well 2 old guys offered to be my date :-D it made me grin! Then we were on our way...

Prom...
We got there...and i waited in the parking garage for a while till VK got there. She looked SOOO Hott!!! LOL. Shes sucha doll!! I love her to death.. Then i mingled for a while...THEN i found Steven,lol.. Me him and Ambera were dancin for quite a while...it was fun! Then prom court was announced. Then David and i danced for a lil...but the songs sucked! Then he kissed me...I was VERY freaked out...it kinda scared me...i didnt know what 2 think at all... But now things r cleared up completley! Then Alysa left...she looked REALLY good that night as well...EVERYONE did...it was truly awesome :-D

*Mad props...thanx Shannon :-D

-Jami

Well having a great break! Hmm...hung w/ Alysa (got her dress,its BEAUTIFUL) Then hung out with Sarah and made some nice home videos :) But on a VERY VERY sad note.Nicholas is going away for a week... im VERY sad! My week is gonna be bad...im gonna miss him greatly! :::sigh::: BUT his hair rocks SOOO hard!!!!! Its not blue anymore...its hott shit now :-D I just got home from Chicago...OMFG! IT was sensational!! It was REALLY REALLY good...the best thing ive seen at Barbra B. MAnn..and ive seen quite a bit of things there. HMM...I made a great decision as well! Hehe...Thanx VK! :-D Ian told me he loved me...that mademe grin, becuz i love him 2...he is Rockin!!

Well then! Today was a rather good day! Had a great day at school :-D... And, David and i talked...I feel SOOO much better... We can tolerate on another now,lol. And there isnt tension. I REALLY enjoyed today ALOT. LMAO and Frankie wrote me a "love letter" lol...not alotta love in it tho. Frankie is sucha great friend! Sarah and Jen r as well :-) I REALLY apreciate them as well... things r akward in guard...i dunno why.lately i feel like its been: Lets hate jami day! But its like an everyday event? Maybe it becuz lately ive been in bad moods...who knows? WEll i got my hair cut & colored.. AND BANGS!!! EEE lol, the bangs r cute...still gettin used to the hair tho, only i seem 2 notice the shortnessness^-^ Im really down about the whole prom issue...I mean...i was REALLY looking forward to it, and now im not going, and everyone that wasnt...is now, and ugh it makes me feel like crying, im gonna be alone that night, and all my friends r gonna be there... :::sigh::: oh well tho... i mean its not like it my prom or anything. I just wanted to get all dressed up and look pretty...is that wrong? 

-Jami

Ugh...This weekend BLOWS! I have done absoloutley NOTHING. UGH! I just wanna like cry or sumthin... Ive been talkin to Ian like this whole weekend...hes a cool kid! lol. Then Sarah came over...and we re-did The Blair Witch Project,lol it was so funny! She spent the night as well. I wanted a tan so bad,lol. But i burnt a CD...thats about all the excitment i had this weekend! Oh and I found a new icon...AND I realized how big of assholes people can be :-( :::sigh::: Things seem to be going downhill latley. Yesterday, I watched Cruel Intentions...and i cried when Sebastion died... hes mad hott! lol. And the story was so...sad. Oh well...he died for love...thats pleasent,lol. Love is SOOOO over-rated...i cant even express that feeling! W/e...

-Jami

LOL!!!

   2day was such an awesome day!!! :-D Well...i worte Frankie a note, lol a "love letter" LMAO... And he wrote me back! Such a nice kid he is...he shakes my pigs ;-D Had fun with him today! And when we were commin back from lunch, Tim squirted frankie in the butt with water, and it looked like he pooed himself,lol. Then hung out with Ian, Nick, and some other kids...I REALLY truly didnt realize how much i like Nick and Ian!! They r soo rockin. And i love them...and Danny, they have been such good friends to me this week when i really needed some good friends. (Thanx u guys) Then i was stranded at school...i mean literally! Missed the bus...Sarah left...So i called Joseph..the life saver he is! lol. So we hung out... hes sucha dork...but he loves me,lmao! I ironed his shirt as well. BUT...me and Jenn had and AWESOME time...we played GTA Vice City...And i won the motorbike race :-) She humped me...we switched purses/clothes...ya know,lol. I love her to death!! Well... Im kinda starting to miss the feeling of having a b/f, cuz i see all these people together..and it just makes me sad... but im not saying i want a b/f, i like things very much how they r... all my guy friends r back in my life..and im getting close to them, and i like it...becuz i miss my guys! Anyhew... Tomorrow Alysa and i r planning on beachin it player! lol Awesome... But i have some bad ass news... I found out like 2 days ago VK is going to USF...and i about cried...im going to miss her SOOO much! Its ridiulious :::sigh:::


*-Mad props to Kendra who made this kick ass journal...love u :-D


-Jami

Today...wasnt so good, well it started off well, and part of 2nd period was good, talked to Trevor for a lil...that kid is awesome!Then the incident with david happened...ugh!! Well I think i realized things r gonna end soon..and rather than to drag it out and be unhappy, to just end it.I hope he soon sees why i did this...it was for the best, for both of us. Maybe next year..or during summer things will change, but this year...i dont think so. Im just going threw alot of things right now, and i need to be more focused on things...and honestly the feeling just wasnt there anymore, maybe it will comme back? But i dont want him to wait around for me...life doesnt work like that, he needs to go out and meet people, and such. I just dont want him to wait for me...that sounds so overly modist, but oh well. I just really care about him, and dont wanna hurt him, even tho i already did, but it wasnt intentional. Well today, Sarah and i didnt have a ride,lol. So we called Joseph, that kid rocks!!
